    <summary>A simple, yet versatile comic book library and reader.</summary>
    <description>YACReader *(Yet Another Comic Reader)* allows you to read, browse, and manage your comics collection.

## Screenshot
![Screenshot](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/yacreader/img/screenshot.jpg)

## Features
* Browse a comic collection using customizable comic flow transitions
* Support for a wide variety of comic files and image types: rar, zip, cbr, cbz, tar, pdf, 7z, cb7, jpeg, gif, png, tiff, and bmp
* Configurable page viewing options: jump to page, double page mode, zoom modes, fullscreen, bookmarks, image rotation, and more
* Image adjustments with brightness, contrast, and gamma sliders

## YACReaderLibrary
* Search through your comic collection
* Track reading progress
* Tag comics using Comic Vine metadata

</description>
